description:
&quot;Herbal medicine is recommended for an unstable heat!&quot;
&quot;I want to be strong since I'm an Omega.&quot; 
Azumi, an apprentice bartender, has been training his body with just this thought in mind. The huge change in his physique and body are the result of his all his hard work, but ironically, they throw his hormone balance out of whack. Now even when he takes a suppressant, his body can suddenly go into heat. In the midst of one of these attacks, he meets a suspicious man, who offers him a Chinese herbal medicine and gives him a business card for a Traditional Chinese Medicine shop...
